      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This car is an absolute dream and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It has been pampered since day one and is in truly spectacular shape\u2014not a scratch or smudge in sight. It drives like a dream and feels brand new. I\u2019m so excited for someone to take this beauty home and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions; I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
