    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2001 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This high-revving unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been fully serviced to ensure optimal torque delivery across the power band. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is structurally sound with professional rear subframe reinforcement already completed\u2014a critical upgrade for this platform. The suspension retains its factory-correct kinematics with fresh bushings and dampers, providing the telepathic steering response these cars are known for. Mechanically pristine with documented compression numbers and a clean DME report, this is a turnkey, collector-grade specimen for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
