    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive attention to detail. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the bodywork look as though it just rolled off the assembly line. There are absolutely no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. The original alloy wheels are pristine, with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with ample tread. Inside, the cabin still carries that distinct new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery remains matte and supple, free from the typical shine or bolstering wear found in used examples. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; it comes with a comprehensive binder of every service record since new, documenting preventative maintenance that exceeds factory recommendations. The engine bay is remarkably clean, showing no signs of leaks or corrosion. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated piece of automotive history ready for its next discerning owner. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom car cover.",
      "price": 46500.0,
